{"tid":1981012,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"14年阿根廷世界盃輸決賽，還有個不利因素是氣候差異","createTime":"2020-04-20T12:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T14:42:49.000Z","uid":173952,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"28b62cb7cc5d0a5c2896ad0a96f83f09226886cb","tid":1981012,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T12:12:12.000Z","msg":"阿根廷與東道主巴西雖然同屬南美洲，但由於該大洲幅員遼闊，受山脈和海洋的影響，兩國的地理氣候其實有很大的差異。<br />\n<br />\n阿根廷的北部屬亞熱帶濕潤氣候，中部屬亞熱帶沙漠氣候，南部為海洋性氣候。<br />\n<br />\n巴西全境大部分為熱帶氣候，北部為赤道多雨氣候，南部為熱帶草原氣候。"},{"pid":"ac63a62ffbe4a1dff74a1d46d16c60bf0369c8ea","tid":1981012,"uid":173952,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T12:17:19.000Z","msg":"美斯又係歐洲踢開波,去到南美洲當然發揮唔到,可以解釋埋點解美洲盃失利"},{"pid":"80e7d24c481688732236d56bd6fa206d42d7b39b","tid":1981012,"uid":52614,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T12:47:25.000Z","msg":"同意，仲有草皮太硬"},{"pid":"873f54c218ac472077aebdd4659bd164fa424170","tid":1981012,"uid":92465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T12:52:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a932cecafaef1e68802c0e0bc577310e1b3c4c4b","tid":1981012,"uid":53855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:00:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5c8376597db816ca128c76d670f000cdc13bb3","tid":1981012,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T14:36:14.000Z","msg":"呢個都係理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eafd31203b27452907b4ea65eb32b38e2eaa70de","tid":1981012,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T14:42:49.000Z","msg":"德國人慣左熱，好能著數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}